metadata.name: Hanging Gardens of Babylon Voxel
metadata.description: This voxel imaginary of my mind from the Hanging Gardens of Babylon. They were one of the Seven Wonders of the Ancient World listed by Hellenic culture. They were described as a remarkable feat of engineering with an ascending series of tiered gardens containing a wide variety of trees, shrubs, and vines, resembling a large green mountain constructed of mud bricks. It was said to have been built in the ancient city of Babylon. (Wikipedia)
